### Hey!
Just a simple landing page for the moment. :)

### Want to help out?
Join us @ the IRC [here](irc://irc.geekshed.net/JBDev)!

### #JBDev developers & Projects
# @rikai
* [JBot](https://github.com/rikai/Showbot)
* [Chrome Extension](https://github.com/rikai/JBAR-Chrome)
* [Firefox Extension](https://github.com/rikai/JBAR-Firefox)

# @MrQweex
* [Callisto](https://github.com/MrQweex/callisto-app/)

# @RobLoach
* [XBMC Plugin](https://github.com/RobLoach/plugin.video.jupiterbroadcasting)

# @covarianttensor
* [Caster Soundboard - Online](https://github.com/covarianttensor/CasterSoundboardOnline/)

# @mailme-gx
* [jsSoundboard](https://github.com/mailme-gx/jsSoundboard)

### Support or Contact
If you have any problems with the site, file an issue on the tracker for this project, send a message to @rikai or come give us a shout on [irc channel](irc://irc.geekshed.net/JBDev).
